<p>9 eqewroun ewV ote qronoi eteqhsan kai palaioV hmerwn ekaqhto ecwn peribolhn wsei ciona kai to tricwma thV kefalhV autou wsei erion leukon kaqaron o qronoV wsei flox puroV</p>
