<p>19 kai eipe moi anqrwpoV eleeinoV ei mh fobou ugiaine andrizou kai iscue kai en tw lalhsai auton met emou iscusa kai eipa lalhsatw o kurioV mou oti eniscuse me</p>
<p>20 kai eipen proV me ginwskeiV ti hlqon proV se kai nun epistreyw diamacesqai meta tou strathgou basilewV twn Perswn kai egw exeporeuomhn kai idou strathgoV Ellhnwn eiseporeueto</p>
