<p>18 kai epoihsan kaqwV eipen kai apekleisan taV quraV tou paradeisou kai exhlqan kata taV plagiaV quraV enegkai ta prostetagmena autaiV kai ouk eidosan touV presbuterouV oti hsan kekrummenoi</p>
